    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted as complete documentation of the current credibility state. Seven of thirteen factors have been assessed, with all assessed factors achieving levels below MRL 5 requirements. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing documented epistemic gaps. The central claim that CFD predictions remain within acceptable uncertainty bounds is supported by three ValidationResults with full provenance to experimental and computational evidence. Monte Carlo UQ provides quantitative margin against clinical threshold. The package is accepted as a complete credibility record acknowledging the identified gaps, to be resolved in subsequent assessment cycles prior to regulatory submission.",
